    <div class="plot_summary ">
            <div class="summary_text" itemprop="description">
                    Gandhi's character is fully explained as a man of nonviolence. Through his patience, he is able to drive the British out of the subcontinent. And the stubborn nature of Jinnah and his commitment towards Pakistan is portrayed.
            </div>
        
    <div class="credit_summary_item">
        <h4 class="inline">Director:</h4>
            <span itemprop="director" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
<a href="/name/nm0000277?ref_=tt_ov_dr"
itemprop='url'><span class="itemprop" itemprop="name">Richard Attenborough</span></a>            </span>
    </div>
    <div class="credit_summary_item">
        <h4 class="inline">Writer:</h4>
            <span itemprop="creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
<a href="/name/nm0109300?ref_=tt_ov_wr"
itemprop='url'><span class="itemprop" itemprop="name">John Briley</span></a>            </span>
    </div>
    <div class="credit_summary_item">
        <h4 class="inline">Stars:</h4>
